nanjing road in shanghai china is one of the world's leading manufacturers of clothing, shoes and accessories. name-brand goods, whether chinese or foreign, tend to be expensive when compared with the unbranded clothing sold in markets throughout the country. see next section for additional comment. chinese brands, similar in look, feel and style to their foreign counterparts, are often an excellent deal. cheap unbranded clothing is also often cheaply manufactured; check the seams and stitching before making a purchase. travelers would be wise to try on any item they wish to purchase as sizes tend to be very erratic. items 